190int ASN1CALL
191copy_OCSPCertID(const OCSPCertID *from, OCSPCertID *to)
192{
193memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
194if(copy_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(from)->hashAlgorithm, &(to)->hashAlgorithm)) goto fail;
195if(der_copy_octet_string(&(from)->issuerNameHash, &(to)->issuerNameHash)) goto fail;
196if(der_copy_octet_string(&(from)->issuerKeyHash, &(to)->issuerKeyHash)) goto fail;
197if(copy_CertificateSerialNumber(&(from)->serialNumber, &(to)->serialNumber)) goto fail;
198return 0;
199fail:
200free_OCSPCertID(to);
201return ENOMEM;
202}
